    {
      "id": "1ae4750c-f3ba-80ca-974a-ffd0f45384fe",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors start with explanation of the constructs and proceed with their quantification. Benchmarking on public datasets shows that the model outperforms other approaches in the literature. Code is also publicly available.",
